%spark
import org.apache.spark.ml.PipelineModel

val testData = spark.createDataFrame(Seq(
	(-12.0,  -4.9),
	( -6.0,  -4.5)
)).toDF("y", "x")

val samePipeline = PipelineModel.load("/model/pipeline")
samePipeline.transform(testData).show()

%pyspark

linreg = spark.table("linreg").toPandas()
plot = linreg.plot.scatter(x='x', y='y')
plot.plot(linreg["x"], linreg["prediction"])

%spark
val quadraticData = data.withColumn("x2", $"x" * $"x")
                        .withColumn("x3", $"x" * $"x" * $"x")
                        .withColumn("x4", $"x" * $"x" * $"x" * $"x")
                        .withColumn("x5", $"x" * $"x" * $"x" * $"x" * $"x")
val polynFeatures = new VectorAssembler()
    .setInputCols(Array("x", "x2", "x3", "x4", "x5"))
    .setOutputCol("features")
val polynPipeline = new Pipeline().setStages(Array(polynFeatures, linreg))
val polynModel = polynPipeline.fit(quadraticData) 
val polynReg = polynModel.stages(1).asInstanceOf[LinearRegressionModel]
println(s"RMSE:  ${polynReg.summary.rootMeanSquaredError}")
polynModel.transform(quadraticData).createOrReplaceTempView("polyn")
